HEADWORD: Comprehensiveness
<hw>Com`pre*hen"sive*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of being
comprehensive; extensiveness of scope.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Compare the beauty and <qex>comprehensiveness</qex> of legends on
ancient coins.</q> <rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Comprehensor</ent>⟦br⟧
